{"data":{"airtable":{"data":{"Person_Lookup":"Simon.2752","Dictionary_Text":"<p>A sorcerer of great repute for his magical arts among the Samaritans ( <a href=\"/passage/?q=Acts+8:9-11\" target=\"_blank\" url=\"/bible/passage.aspx?q=Acts+8:9-11&amp;t=niv\">Acts 8:9-11</a> ). He afterwards became a professed convert to the faith under the preaching of Philip the deacon and evangelist (12,13). His profession was, however, soon found to be hollow. His conduct called forth from Peter a stern rebuke ( <a href=\"/passage/?q=Acts+8:18-23\" target=\"_blank\" url=\"/bible/passage.aspx?q=Acts+8:18-23&amp;t=niv\">8:18-23</a> ). From this moment he disappears from the Church's history. The term \"Simony,\" as denoting the purchase for money of spiritual offices, is derived from him.","Aliases":"Simon","Father":null,"Has_Been_to":[{"data":{"Place_Lookup":"Samaria.1022","ESV_name":"Samaria"}}],"Events":[{"data":{"Event_Name":"Philip preaches in Samaria","Start_Year":[{"data":{"Year":"34"}}]}}],"Personal_network":[{"data":{"Person_Lookup":"Philip.2347","Name":"Philip"}},{"data":{"Person_Lookup":"Peter.2745","Name":"Simon"}},{"data":{"Person_Lookup":"John.1677","Name":"John"}}],"Member_of_Groups":null,"Verses":[{"data":{"Verse_Num":"9","Book":[{"data":{"Canonical_Order":44,"Osis_Name":"Acts"}}],"Chapter":[{"data":{"Chapter_Lookup":"Acts.8"}}]}},{"data":{"Verse_Num":"18","Book":[{"data":{"Canonical_Order":44,"Osis_Name":"Acts"}}],"Chapter":[{"data":{"Chapter_Lookup":"Acts.8"}}]}},{"data":{"Verse_Num":"24","Book":[{"data":{"Canonical_Order":44,"Osis_Name":"Acts"}}],"Chapter":[{"data":{"Chapter_Lookup":"Acts.8"}}]}},{"data":{"Verse_Num":"13","Book":[{"data":{"Canonical_Order":44,"Osis_Name":"Acts"}}],"Chapter":[{"data":{"Chapter_Lookup":"Acts.8"}}]}}]}}},"pageContext":{"lookup":"Simon.2752"}}